{"tid":1288524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔好中計]反送中已成反政府運動核心","createTime":"2019-07-05T16:10:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T05:18:40.000Z","uid":199108,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"18a21e62e3e31a6f4d77eff33ddf344492c01103","tid":1288524,"uid":199108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T16:10:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">反送中令到好多港豬/中立嘅人出嚟<br />\n好喇大和解喇<br />\n然後呢?<br />\n乜香港得送中一個問題咋咩???</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n難得有咁多<span style=\"color: red;\">港豬/中產/淺黃</span>支持<br />\n你諗住俾佢哋停?<br />\n<br />\n哩類人唔可以<span style=\"color: red;\">去得太深</span> (好多已接受暫緩)<br />\n但係可以<span style=\"color: red;\">去得好廣</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">普教中<br />\n單程證<br />\n海外醫生<br />\n自由行</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢啲都係香港嘅問題<br />\n點解我哋唔可以食住個勢<br />\n用突然爆發嘅民意搞掂埋佢哋?</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">(我特登唔講真普選/明日大愚 因為港豬/中產/淺黃嘅腦袋同精力唔足夠佢哋諗啲長遠/結構性嘅問題)<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n但係對於切身嘅問題,我覺得我哋可以食住個勢逐項逐項解決<br />\n<br />\n當然我唔奢望呢2000000民意會去到好盡<br />\n正如佢哋好多都接收咗&quot;暫緩&quot;<br />\n但係我覺得我哋可以好好利用而家全民議政嘅氣氛<br />\n喺反送中淡化後重提其他議題<br />\n唔可以俾&quot;反送中&quot;騎劫呢場運動<br />\n咁先係社運嘅&quot;遍地開花&quot;<br />\n<br />\n今次好多人都話家中長輩變黃<br />\n如果focus 放晒喺反送中<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">實在係益咗呢個政府</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n唔係叫大家放軟手腳<br />\n係想呢場星星之火蔓延</span><br />\n<br />\n嚟緊一年,趁政治氣氛濃烈,唔同議題都要重提<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">要政府每一項都讓步<br />\n少少都好</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n唔好俾佢停 唔好俾港共休息<br />\nWe never forget</span>"},{"pid":"cf722c54ba1a521875509cf1560fd4eee8e4c039","tid":1288524,"uid":199108,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T16:33:30.000Z","msg":"今次反送中同雨革除咗<span style=\"color: red;\">去大台</span><br />\n另一個特色就係<span style=\"color: red;\">針對個別政策</span><br />\n<br />\n有真普選的確一勞永逸<br />\n但係逐次逐次抗爭似乎係大勢所催<br />\n<br />\n太接近政治層面(政改)嘅訴求太過離地<br />\n好多人掛住返工返學未必會去諗得咁深"},{"pid":"b78d8220d98925d108edd2f22eeeb446469d1156","tid":1288524,"uid":199108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T16:35:31.000Z","msg":"相反如果我哋可以用連登嘅力量<br />\n將唔同切身議題逐一放大同宣傳<br />\n會有好多人和應"},{"pid":"9508967c7404325fb35d685181a79c0d51c1dc65","tid":1288524,"uid":199108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T16:36:09.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"a67286f7aa3a93d5a3b291837fbc5a70a315fab3","tid":1288524,"uid":199108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T16:38:54.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"d12a6544da43322da2d2604e798f940a809f221c","tid":1288524,"uid":199108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T16:45:37.000Z","msg":"反送中嘅特色:<br />\n去大台<br />\n單一議題抗爭<br />\n實在/切身"},{"pid":"36c4ea810c482022d44e2f45fab8fe1822788a6a","tid":1288524,"uid":199108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T16:51:43.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"a3aa4f1eddae3f9e8a63aad7c9d16df6de09907b","tid":1288524,"uid":199108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T16:59:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f85b7458b0cdcc47ed05e9ded12f0457d11cc20a","tid":1288524,"uid":199108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T16:59:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1f870991ed04fbd8b7d1b44baac02922dbf8dfce","tid":1288524,"uid":199108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:00:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b4dfa26178575152bb6c098e6ddb2514199a7d53","tid":1288524,"uid":199108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:02:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2efd0b2d4a00a14aaaca3a6620fbb9f66aaea399","tid":1288524,"uid":199108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:04:01.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"169968db8332d678f7e023c1b55f8ac97c479642","tid":1288524,"uid":229369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:39:15.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講<img src=\"/assets